# Build artifacts and the auto-healed lockfile for this nested bench
# workspace. Cargo.lock is ignored for the same reason as the test
# fixtures: its litmask path-dep pins the workspace version, which
# `cargo set-version` does not reach across the workspace boundary, so a
# committed lockfile would go stale on every release bump and dirty the
# tree on the next bench run.
/target
/Cargo.lock
